data.title: Telecommunication
data.meta_description: Format numbers - Free ebook download as Text File (.txt), PDF File (.pdf) or read book online for free. This document lists 376 enterprise numbers assigned by IANA to various organizations, along with the organization names. Some of the early numbers are assigned to research institutions like MIT, BBN Technologies, and Carnegie Mellon. Later numbers are assigned to large technology companies like Cisco, HP, IBM, Microsoft, Intel, and 3Com. The document provides a historical record of the early assignments of enterprise numbers.
